{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/floral_detail.png?t=1728922408\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Embark on a Treacherous Pilgrimage</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For hundreds of years, the Mountain Folk have used their powers of <strong>Astral Projection</strong> to travel vast distances. But <strong>Mae</strong> is different\u2013her spirit travel is limited by a <strong>tether</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mae is of age to join a traditional <strong>pilgrimage</strong> to a sacred temple called the <strong>Fount of Souls</strong>. While her peers effortlessly make the journey by spirit flight, Mae is forced to take <strong>the long way</strong>.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join Mae in her <strong>valiant struggle</strong> to prove herself. Become master of your tether, conquer the many <strong>challenging obstacles</strong> on your path, and unlock the <strong>true power</strong> of the Fount of Souls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/extras/KSHeroGif01.gif?t=1728922408\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master Spirit Flight with Six Different Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Progressively unlock <strong>new spirit abilities</strong> throughout the game. <strong>Gather</strong> <strong>and use</strong> different <strong>medicines</strong> to change <strong>how your spirit interacts</strong> with the environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover Hundreds of Hidden Secrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scour every corner for <strong>hidden rooms</strong> and <strong>alternate paths</strong> with advanced obstacles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore Hub Areas and Interact with NPCs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pass through villages filled with <strong>people you can talk to</strong> and several <strong>buildings you can enter</strong>. Learn more about the<strong> lore</strong> and discover <strong>Atropa Blossoms</strong> when you complete <strong>small quests</strong> for villagers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Pure Platforming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No weapons, combat, monsters, powerups, or skill trees. Just pure, challenging platforming - designed around exploring new movement systems to achieve satisfying leaps and bounds across levels. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tough but Forgiving</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The levels are difficult, but checkpoints are frequent, allowing you to quickly learn through failure and use your practice to satisfyingly tackle each trial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A nearly perfect day...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/16f8b0549b7e064c945963d7dcea72d32538ee65.jpg"},{"name":"Here we go!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/901a0ed21e4332292cac9c159675005ce019966c.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint, you are a true friend.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/c180327b7065d8d31dd12c94c3a617e5f163e6a0.jpg"},{"name":"TetherGeist Soul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/2ae1f0ff1bd88b7b3749768fd78b3fa0b90bb414.jpg"},{"name":"Takin' on the jellies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/60aca6d4711fae5ed1d333554763571f3775e2d6.jpg"},{"name":"Completionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3273110/2f8623fa003f86921f62987d697a7cfc9ce3104c.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728922408","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st